вҠў greet
  given name
  yield message
  вҲҙ Greet the person called В«nameВ» with a warm hello.
  вҠЁ message contains В«nameВ»
  вҠЁ message is exactly one sentence

вҠў wrap
  given greetвҶ’message
  yield text, emoji
  вҲҙ Take В«greetвҶ’messageВ» as text and choose an emoji that fits.
  вҠЁ text = В«greetвҶ’messageВ»
  вҠЁ emoji is a single unicode emoji character
